# Manifestation Log: styles.css

**Date:** 2026-03-07
**Spore:** /spores/_food/prompt.md
**Action:** Responsive design enhancement + font size increase

## Changes Made

### Font Size Increases
- Base body font: 18px → 20px
- Logo: 1.5rem → 1.8rem
- Tagline: 1.3rem → 1.5rem
- Hero description: 1.1rem → 1.25rem
- Section H2: 2rem → 2.4rem
- Feature H3: 1.1rem → 1.25rem
- Feature paragraph: 0.95rem → 1.05rem
- Line height: 1.7 → 1.8

### Responsive Design Enhancements
- Added new breakpoint at 1024px for tablet optimization
- Enhanced 768px breakpoint with:
  - Better navigation stacking
  - Smaller nav link fonts
  - Improved hero scaling
  - Adjusted section padding
  - Left-aligned text on mobile
  - Single-column feature grid
- Added 480px breakpoint for small mobile
- Added fluid typography with clamp()

## Rationale
The prompt requested "more responsive design, fonts a little bit bigger". The changes increase all font sizes by approximately 10-15% while adding comprehensive responsive breakpoints to ensure proper display across all device sizes.
